collectible.name: Green Apple
collectible.author: 0xae369b72d56b843719628c7c622d925843b5bf25
collectible.description:
Amazing Devya's Green Apple character is now a wearable. You can now be a green apple or have it as a pet friend by your side in cryptovoxels.

                                                                              
 Devya has a unique way of drawing her characters with emotions. Devya created the green apple on paper in June 2021. Devya's mom made the voxel green apple as commemorative wearable for Amazing Devya's first ever winter wonderland Christmas party 2021. It was a part of holiday build contest and it won a honorary mention, thanks to the green apple. Green apple is a happy apple that spreads smiles everywhere it goes.
